title: #132 - Ari Shaffir, Duncan Trussell, & ME
description: Live from the Just For Laughs Comedy Festival in Montreal comedians Ari Shaffir & Duncan Trussell sit down with me infront of a live audience and talk about being generous lovers, death, and drugs.
